OL,3,CGardener who took truckload of
OL,4,C'ammunition' to riot jailed
OL,6,FA self-employed gardener who drove a
OL,7,Ftruckload of debris to a hotel where
OL,8,Frioters were attacking police has been
OL,9,Fjailed.
OL,11,FJake Turton was filmed arriving at the
OL,12,Fscene - close to the Holiday Inn
OL,13,FExpress in Rotherham - in a Ford
OL,14,FRanger with wood and other scrap items
OL,15,Fon the back.
OL,17,FFootage from a police helicopter
OL,18,Fshowed the rioters throwing items from
OL,19,Fthe truck at officers.
