OL,3,CGardener who took truckload of
OL,4,C'ammunition' to riot jailed
OL,6,FSome of the wood was used to fuel
OL,7,Ffires around the hotel, which was
OL,8,Fhousing hundreds of asylum seekers.
OL,10,FProsecutors said he had driven his
OL,11,Ftruck to the scene deliberately to
OL,12,Fprovide ammunition and weapons, but
OL,13,FTurton's defence barristers said the
OL,14,Frioters "helped themselves" to the
OL,15,Fwood and the defendant did not
OL,16,Factively participate in the violence.
OL,18,FTurton, 38, of Darfield, Barnsley,
OL,19,Fpreviously pleaded guilty to violent
OL,20,Fdisorder over the incident on 4 August.
